Output docs/vhs/demo.gif

Require go

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontFamily "IosevkaTerm NFM"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1440
Set Height 1280
Set Padding 24
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set Framerate 30
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set BorderRadius 10
Set Margin 20
Set MarginFill "#0b1c26"

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 250ms
Type "mage demo"
Enter
Show
Sleep 5s
